organization.description:
Psychotherapy and Counseling services offered include individual therapy, family therapy, child/adolescent therapy, and group therapy. Psychological Assessment and Testing services offered involving behavior and school problems; learning disabilities in children and adults; intellectual assessment (developmental disabilities and gifted); personality assessment; and infant assessment.

Staff includes doctoral students in clinical psychology working under the supervision of University of Miami faculty.
organization.name: UNIVERSITY OF MIAMI - PSYCHOLOGICAL SERVICES CENTER (PSC)
